    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Ante Factum</h2><i>This is the studio's first game and we are interested in your opinion!<br>Feel free to write a comment, even and especially if you don't like something.<br>Have fun!</i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >​Description</h2>The guy, whose name is shrouded in mystery, gets into an unpleasant life situation.<br>The owner of the company where he worked for a long time left this business.<br>The new head forced him to work 24/7 for several months. <br>After – all the work of our kid was in vain. Or not?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132950/extras/ENDME_GENRE.GIF?t=1725483210\" /></span><br><strong>Quest.</strong> Collect socks, hack security protocols and spend time at nothingdoingness.<br><strong>Shooter.</strong> Check your eardrums and friendship with hedgehogs at the same time.<br><strong>Platformer.</strong> Finally it'll take you out or it'll be defeated by your skill and self-confidence.<br><br>Gameplay time ~40 minutes (fast), ~90 minutes (normal).<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Post Scriptum</h2><i>I'd like to thank several people who inspired, supported,<br>hindered and harmed me on the way making this game.<br>Thank you.</i>",
